item.description:
GitHub rate limit exceeded To avoid exceeding GitHubs rate limit we suggest to generate a personal access token in your GitHub settings and set it as an environment variable:
Mac/Linux Windows export GITHUB_API_TOKEN=&lt;your_api_token&gt;
set GITHUB_API_TOKEN=&lt;your_api_token&gt; or Set environment variable via system settings GITHUB_API_TOKEN=&lt;your_api_token&gt;
After you have set the ENV consider to restart VS Code.
It is important that VS Code has access to this ENV during the postCreateCommand inside the devcontainer.
